                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">One positive aspect of</span> these platforms <span class="key-expression">is that</span> they provide valuable networking opportunities. <span class="key-expression">In particular</span>, professionals can connect with colleagues and potential employers, <span class="key-expression">consequently</span> expanding their career prospects.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">It is also worth noting that</span> social media serves as a powerful tool for raising awareness about important social issues, <span class="key-expression">hence</span> mobilizing communities for positive change.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Slide 3: Arguments AGAINST -->
                    <div class="carousel-slide">
                        <div class="section">
                            <span class="section-label against">ARGUMENTS AGAINST</span>
