                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">The obvious drawback of</span> social media <span class="key-expression">is that</span> it raises serious privacy concerns. <span class="key-expression">For instance</span>, personal data is often collected and sold to advertisers without explicit consent.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">One effective way to deal with this</span> problem <span class="key-expression">is</span> to implement stricter regulations, <span class="key-expression">although/even though</span> this remains a complex challenge.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Slide 4: Conclusion -->
                    <div class="carousel-slide">
                        <div class="section">
                            <span class="section-label">CONCLUSION</span>
