                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-slide">
                        <div class="section">
                            <span class="section-label for">ARGUMENTS FOR</span>
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">The main argument in favour of</span> online shopping <span class="key-expression">is that</span> it offers unparalleled convenience. <span class="key-expression">For instance</span>, consumers can browse and purchase products 24/7 from the comfort of their homes.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">One positive aspect of</span> e-commerce platforms <span class="key-expression">is that</span> they provide access to a wider range of products. <span class="key-expression">In other words</span>, shoppers can compare prices across multiple retailers, <span class="key-expression">consequently</span> finding better deals.</p>
