                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">The obvious drawback of</span> e-commerce <span class="key-expression">is that</span> it contributes to environmental concerns through excessive packaging and delivery emissions. <span class="key-expression">That is to say</span>, each individual delivery increases carbon footprint.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">One clear solution would be</span> to consolidate deliveries or choose sustainable shipping options, <span class="key-expression">although/even though</span> not all retailers offer these alternatives.</p>
