                    <div class="carousel-slide">
                        <div class="section">
                            <span class="section-label for">ARGUMENTS FOR</span>
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">The main advantage of</span> travelling <span class="key-expression">is that</span> it exposes people to diverse cultures and perspectives. <span class="key-expression">For example</span>, experiencing different traditions firsthand fosters greater understanding and tolerance.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">One positive aspect of</span> exploring new destinations <span class="key-expression">is that</span> it enhances personal growth and independence. <span class="key-expression">In particular</span>, navigating unfamiliar environments builds confidence and problem-solving skills.</p>
