                        <div class="section">
                            <span class="section-label against">ARGUMENTS AGAINST</span>
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">The argument against</span> frequent air travel <span class="key-expression">is that</span> it significantly contributes to climate change. <span class="key-expression">This is largely due to/owing to</span> the substantial carbon emissions from aviation.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">The obvious drawback of</span> mass tourism <span class="key-expression">is that</span> it can damage natural environments and cultural heritage sites. <span class="key-expression">For instance</span>, overcrowding threatens the preservation of historical landmarks.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section">
                            <p class="section-text"><span class="key-expression">By far the best way to tackle</span> this issue <span class="key-expression">is</span> to promote sustainable tourism practices, <span class="key-expression">although/even though</span> implementation requires global cooperation.</p>
